No. 09-1042. Bhupendra K. Shah, Petitioner v. New York State Department of Civil Service, et al. 559 U.S. 1116, 130 S. Ct. 2429,

176 L. Ed. 2d 941,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 3818, May 3, 2010.

Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice So-tomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 341 Fed. Appx. 670.
